01:10:09,272 --> 01:10:11,932
Well, maybe I don't
see it that way.

820
01:10:12,442 --> 01:10:14,982
Oh, so it's back
to pretending we're human again?

821
01:10:15,442 --> 01:10:18,782
Come on. Spare me
the Uncle Tom routine, OK?

822
01:10:19,242 --> 01:10:22,042
