They're afraid of you.

826
01:10:29,842 --> 01:10:31,092
And they should be.

827
01:10:31,592 --> 01:10:32,132
You're an animal.

828
01:10:32,632 --> 01:10:34,632
You're a fuckin'
maniac.

829
01:10:37,602 --> 01:10:38,762
Look at 'em.

830
01:10:39,142 --> 01:10:41,062
They're cattle,

831
01:10:41,472 --> 01:10:43,022
