aah!

858
01:12:39,822 --> 01:12:41,032
Go home.

859
01:12:44,492 --> 01:12:45,202
It was simple.

860
01:12:45,662 --> 01:12:47,622
Why do vampires
need to drink blood?

861
01:12:48,082 --> 01:12:50,082
'Cause their own blood
can't sustain haemoglobin.

862
01:12:50,502 --> 01:12:51,922
Right. So it's
a genetic defect,

863
01:12:52,422 --> 01:12:53,132
just like
haemolytic anaemia.

864
01:12:53,582 --> 01:12:55,672
That means that
we have to treat it

865
01:12:56,132 --> 01:12:56,962
with gene therapy,

866
01:12:57,512 --> 01:12:59,512
rewrite the victim's DNA
with a retrovirus.

867
01:12:59,762 --> 01:13:00,932
They've been using it
on sickle cell anaemia.

868
01:13:02,472 --> 01:13:03,552
Are you sure
that's safe?

869
01:13:04,012 --> 01:13:05,052
I have no idea,

870
01:13:05,512 --> 01:13:07,932
but I don't have
a choice, do I?

871
01:13:09,562 --> 01:13:11,442
You actually think
this could work?

872
01:13:11,942 --> 01:13:13,442
