873
01:13:13,902 --> 01:13:15,192
yes.

874
01:13:15,652 --> 01:13:17,732
On Blade,
I'm not so sure.

875
01:13:18,322 --> 01:13:19,532
See, he didn't
contract vampirism

876
01:13:19,942 --> 01:13:21,402
from a bite
like I did.

877
01:13:21,822 --> 01:13:22,992
