of the daywalker.

904
01:17:00,912 --> 01:17:03,542
You're the chosen one.

905
01:17:07,132 --> 01:17:08,422
Listen to me, Blade.

906
01:17:09,962 --> 01:17:11,472
You can't
go after him.

907
01:17:11,922 --> 01:17:13,222
Bullshit.

908
01:17:13,762 --> 01:17:15,512
If Frost gets
his hands on you,

909
01:17:16,012 --> 01:17:18,432
it's all over.

910
01:17:21,352 --> 01:17:24,062
There'll be armies
of the motherfuckers.

911
