931
01:20:49,592 --> 01:20:51,052
like you need to
release something.

932
01:20:52,092 --> 01:20:52,882
You know?

933
01:20:53,262 --> 01:20:54,342
Blade not...

934
01:20:55,652 --> 01:20:57,862
givin' it to you
maybe.

935
01:20:59,072 --> 01:20:59,942
I don't know.
I just...

