01:21:00,532 --> 01:21:03,492
I see such
a beautiful woman.

937
01:21:05,202 --> 01:21:06,452
Great skin.

938
01:21:09,202 --> 01:21:11,002
I'd like to see you
happy, that's all.

939
01:21:11,412 --> 01:21:14,622
Is this the part where
you offer to turn me?

940
01:21:16,132 --> 01:21:18,252
Well, it's either that
or a body bag.

941
01:21:18,632 --> 01:21:20,002
Go ahead.

942
01:21:20,462 --> 01:21:21,512
Bite me.

943
01:21:22,012 --> 01:21:24,552
I'll just cure myself.

944
01:21:25,132 --> 01:21:26,052
I did it before,

945
01:21:26,552 --> 01:21:27,762
and I can do it again.

946
01:21:28,262 --> 01:21:29,642
There is no cure,
baby.

947
01:21:30,102 --> 01:21:31,272
There is if you've
been bit,

948
01:21:31,722 --> 01:21:34,982
if you were once human.

949
01:21:40,402 --> 01:21:41,402
How'd you get
that scar, Deacon?

950
01:21:41,822 --> 01:21:42,862
A born vampire

951
01:21:43,282 --> 01:21:45,652
would have the power
to regenerate from birth.

952
01:21:46,162 --> 01:21:48,912
You must've gotten scarred
before you were turned.

953
01:21:49,412 --> 01:21:50,332
Isn't that right?

954
01:21:50,782 --> 01:21:53,792
Vampires like you
aren't a species.

955
01:21:54,252 --> 01:21:56,962
You're just... infected,
a virus...

956
01:21:57,462 --> 01:21:59,142
a sexually transmitted
disease.

957
01:21:59,602 --> 01:22:00,682
I'll tell you
what we are, sister.

958
01:22:01,102 --> 01:22:03,222
We're the top of
the fuckin' food chain.

959
01:22:03,722 --> 01:22:05,352
The Blood God's coming.
And after tonight,

960
01:22:05,852 --> 01:22:07,272
you people
are fuckin' history.

961
01:22:08,982 --> 01:22:10,062
He's a hurricane,

962
01:22:10,522 --> 01:22:12,232
an act of God.

963
01:22:12,612 --> 01:22:14,032
Anyone caught
in his path

964
01:22:14,492 --> 01:22:15,572
